  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "Season the trout fillets with salt, black pepper, and thyme.",
    "Brush the grill or grill pan with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Add the trout fillets to the grill and cook for 3-4 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, heat the avocado oil in a small skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the pickled onions and capers to the skillet and cook until crispy, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in the paprika and cook for an additional minute.",
    "To serve, place the cooked trout fillets on a plate and top with the crispy pickled onion mixture and a sprinkle of parsley.",
    "Garnish with additional parsley if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
